            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Paying for dofollow links violates Google's spam policies. Sponsored content is allowed but must use rel=sponsored or rel=nofollow attributes. Paying editorial fees for placement is a link scheme regardless of how it is described.</p></div></div>
